dc_title_s: Grayscale shaded relief map of Israel
dc_description_s: Geophysical Institute of Israel. Companion text: Geological framework of the Levant. Volume I: Cyprus and Syria. Volume II: The Levantine Basin and Israel / John K. Hall; Valey A. Krasheninnikov; Francis Hirsch; Chaim Benjamini; Akiva Flexer. Jerusalem: Historical Productions-Hall. 2005. North Decimal Degree 33.3333. South Decimal Degree 29.5000. East Decimal Degree 35.8833.
